## 📋 Requirements

### 🔧 Hardware Requirements
- ESP32 Microcontroller  
- MQ-3 Alcohol Sensor  
- MPU6050 Accelerometer & Gyroscope  
- IR Sensor / Push Switch (Helmet Detection)  
- Buzzer / LED for Alerts  
- Jumper Wires  
- Breadboard / PCB (KiCad Designed)  
- Rechargeable Battery / Power Supply  

---

### 💻 Software Requirements
- Arduino IDE  
- ESP32 Board Package (ESP32 Core installed in Arduino IDE)  
- Required Libraries:
  - Wire.h (for I2C communication)
  - MPU6050 library
  - WiFi.h / BluetoothSerial.h (for communication)
- Serial Monitor (for debugging)

---

### ⚙️ System Requirements
- Laptop / PC for programming and monitoring  
- USB Cable for ESP32 programming  
- Stable power source  

---

### 🌐 Optional Requirements (Advanced Features)
- GPS Module (for location tracking)  
- GSM Module (for SMS alerts)  
- Mobile App / Dashboard  
- Cloud Platform (for data logging)  
